title: Dan Snyder News, NBA Outlook 2022
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring Wosny Lambre! On today’s show: What's your reaction to the latest Dan Snyder news? Who do you have more faith in to get back to the finals: the Celtics or Warriors? Which small market team that went all-in is more likely to break through this year: The T-Wolves or the Cavs? Who do you think has more pressure on them this season: James Harden or Ben Simmons? Plus, how do you think the looming Victor Wembanyama sweepstakes is going to shape this season?
